  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Clinic Assistant (Office Hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a detail-oriented and organized Clinic Assistant to support daily operations at our healthcare clinic. The role involves managing administrative tasks, coordinating documentation, and ensuring smooth clinic operations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Provide daily support to the department, include preparing of the documents and reports</p>\n<p>· Receive, screen and register patients into the clinical system</p>\n<p>· Address any inquires / feedback or any other concerns from patients</p>\n<p>· Arranges for prescribed laboratory tests, specialist referrals and/or any other procedures</p>\n<p>· Obtains and verifies patient billing information before collecting payment</p>\n<p>· Assist in maintaining the cleanliness of all unit facilities, equipment and tidy the general appearance of the counter</p>\n<p>· Perform data entry and closure of daily settlement</p>\n<p>· Handle incoming phone calls and making of appointments</p>\n<p>· Any other adhoc duties as assigned by Clinic Manager</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Related working experience in healthcare and understanding of medical terminology/ abbreviations/ jargon will be added advantage</p>\n<p>· Strong computer skills. Proficient in MS Office Advantage</p>\n<p>· Meticulous, eye for details, precise, organised and efficient</p>\n<p>· Good communication and interpersonal skill</p>\n<p>· Effective team player and able to work in fast paced environment</p>\n<p>· 5.5 days work week (Monday to Friday; Half Saturday)</p>\n<p>· Location: Biopolis Buona Vista</p>",
